        <h2 class="text-white" data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:adx0wi">Acceptance and Accuracy</h2>
        <p data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:zhj1ok">By using the ParOne Service, Website, or Apps, you agree, without limitation or qualification, to be bound by, and to comply with, these Terms and Conditions and any other posted guidelines or rules applicable to any website or App where the ParOne Service is found.</p>

        <h2 class="text-white" data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:adx0wj">Conditions and Restrictions of Use</h2>
        <h3 class="text-white" data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:n6kn0z">Termination</h3>
        <p data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:zhj1oj">Use of the ParOne Service is subject to compliance with these Terms and Conditions. You acknowledge and agree that ParOne may terminate and/or suspend your access to any portion of the ParOne Service should you fail to comply with the Terms and Conditions.</p>

        <h3 class="text-white" data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:n6kn10">Access to Content</h3>
        <p data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:zhj1nx">Please be aware that the majority of the content found on or through the ParOne service is for general audiences, but there may be certain adult or mature content. Where there is mature or adult content, individuals who are less than 18 years of age may not access such content.</p>

        <h2 class="text-white" data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:adx0wk">Registration and Privacy</h2>
        <p data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:zhj1nw">Certain of the ParOne Services will require the user to register and provide certain data. You represent and warrant that the information about yourself is true, accurate, current, and complete.</p>
        <p data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:zhj1nv">ParOne reserves the right to use and reuse all registration and other personally identifiable user information subject to the ParOne Privacy Policy, which is found at <a href="/privacy/" class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300" data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:sdl4yu">/privacy</a>.</p>

        <h2 class="text-white" data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:adx0wl">Prohibited Conduct</h2>
        <p data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:zhj1nu">You agree that you will not use ParOne Services to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:wf5l9k">Upload or transmit content that is unlawful, harmful, threatening, or abusive.</li>
          <li data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:wf5l8y">Impersonate any person or entity.</li>
          <li data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:wf5l8x">Upload content that infringes any patent, trademark, or copyright.</li>
          <li data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:wf5l8w">Interfere with or disrupt the Services or servers.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-white" data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:adx0wm">Contact Information</h2>
        <p data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:zhj1nt">In the event that you believe that Content published on or through the ParOne Service violates these terms, please contact us at:</p>
        <p data-ps="src/pages/terms.astro:zhj1ns">
